headline: Breadkrumb Launches as the First AI-Powered Travel App to Curate Trips from Trusted Friends’ Travel Experiences
summary: Atlanta, Georgia, Aug. 21, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- According to an Accenture study, 64% of travelers feel overwhelmed by the sheer volume of options when planning. Breadkrumb, the first AI-powered mobile app built around a traveler’s trusted inner circle, aims to cut through that noise by transforming personal recommendations into curated, confidence-driven itineraries.
